Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:03.60,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Do you know where I'm going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:05.80,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,I don't know either,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.65,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,because I'm about to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:11.18,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Is that an evolved human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:14.60,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,You can think that if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Don't you need a body to to be a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.54,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,Some people have bodies that aren't necessarily human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:22.67,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,And me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:24.66,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Am I not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.93,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,Lain is Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:29.45,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What does it mean to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.75,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,If I have a body, does that make me human?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.57,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.08,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Are you trying to blend in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.93,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,You need a body if you're going to live in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.35,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Suicide would be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:44.46,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,You're better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Don't I need my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What if I need it someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.28,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:55.52,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,But you don't need a body to live in the Wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.24,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I'll need the memories of a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.41,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What about the memories of an aging body?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.09,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What if my beliefs change?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.53,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,Do they need to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:08.40,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:12.58,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Hey, Lain, what do I need to get on the Wired?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.25,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,Will and existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.52,antilain,Antilain,0,0,0,,The rest is just data.
